column2: SELECT u.up_name as name, s.specobjid, s.ra, s.dec, s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  p.objID, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN SpecObjAll s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN PhotoTag p ON p.objID = s.bestObjID &&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
